n be\ncalculated locally. Finally, we analyze the repeated execution of the proposed\nD2D trading mechanism in multiple rounds and determine the best trading\nfrequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2020 08:30:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 14:39:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-31"}
