R has been applied to gain new insights into the\nstructure of organic, hybrid and inorganic materials with applications in\nfields, such as health, energy, catalysis,optoelectronics etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2020 09:03:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-21"}
