ns between\nspectroscopy and asteroseismology. We compared the seismic gravities with those\nbased on Gaia parallaxes to find an offset which is similar to other studies\nthat have used asteroseismology. Our catalogue also includes spectroscopic\nchemical abundances and radial velocities, as well as indicators for possible\nbinary detections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2020 15:25:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Jul 2020 18:32:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
